  3. Gate: all of the above runs only when `TOOL_DIGEST_PLUGIN_DRIFT in {shadow, prefer}`; `prefer` is a no-op for topic selection until the flip criterion is met.
- Then run one forced digest (`uv run python run_tool_digest.py --force --no-post`) to verify the JSON capture and diff machinery end-to-end without touching Telegram or the staged debate.

